	| Unfortunately, the rest of the dashboard shows a lot of sensitive member data, you'll just have to take my word that it looks great. The user facing side of the reservation system was integrated into Domi's Squarespace site and is shown below. I used the <a href='http://tympanus.net/codrops/2013/05/21/natural-language-form-with-custom-input-elements/'>Natural Language Form demo</a> from Codrops to make it easy to use for the members. When the server receives a request it checks to see if that room is availble at that time, if not it lets the user know who's already snagged it.
